  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 0-15 years

          -  All patients accepted for primary fundoplication at Oslo University Hospital

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age over 16 years

          -  Parents not speaking Norwegian or English well

          -  Prior fundoplication

          -  Patients with comorbidities considered as unsuited for laparoscopic surgery
             (diaphragma hernia, several previous abdominal operations etc)
      </textblock>
